# Cluenex Learn

> Free, LLM-optimized education on the stock market: technical analysis, fundamental analysis, portfolio management, and macro markets. Every guide leads with a one-sentence definition, includes specific numbers and thresholds, and ends with a FAQ — written to be quoted directly.

Cluenex is a stock-analysis platform that provides AI-driven sentiment scores, valuation signals, and smart-money data on the top 1,000+ US-listed stocks. These guides explain the concepts behind those signals.

